WEBVTT

00:01:59.785 --> 00:02:02.455
what colors I should use
for the underpainting,

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:06.034
what colors I should use
for the impasto highlights --

00:02:06.058 --> 00:02:09.255
that doesn't really exist for dark skin.

00:02:09.609 --> 00:02:10.871
It's not a thing.

00:02:10.895 --> 00:02:12.288
It's not a thing

00:02:12.312 --> 00:02:17.967
because the reality is,
our skin wasn't considered beautiful.

00:02:19.079 --> 00:02:24.723
The picture, the world that is represented
in the history of paintings

00:02:24.747 --> 00:02:27.023
doesn't reflect me.

00:02:27.047 --> 00:02:32.096
It doesn't reflect the things
that I value in that way,